				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				To clarify...if you are too close to the mob when you cast mesmerization, yes, you too will also be mezzed.  However, your party members will not be mezzed.  Found out first hand fighting mobs near a stairhead in runnyeye.  Mobs of three to five were pulled to a smallish area, i as an enchanter stood back and mezzed the mob.  My group was on assist and because i was too close to the mob I was mezzing I too got stunned sometimes.  So...make sure you stand far enough back, and mezz will perform beautifully.
